      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-num                =    01
                     move  "I"            to   rr-tip-inv
           else if   v-num                =    02
                     move  "F"            to   rr-tip-inv
           else      move  spaces         to   rr-tip-inv             .
       acc-tip-inv-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
