           if        rf-dcp-tip-pro       not  = 01
                     go to car-dti-dcp-ubi-200.
       car-dti-dcp-ubi-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione buffer giacenze per ubica-   *
      *                  * zione                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PU"                 to   d-sld-ubi-tip-ope      .
           move      rr-dat-inv           to   d-sld-ubi-dat-ela      .
           move      01                   to   d-sld-ubi-cod-dpz      .
           move      01                   to   d-sld-ubi-tip-mag      .
