           perform   det-sld-ubi-cll-000  thru det-sld-ubi-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scrittura per ubicazione           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-gia-ubi-ctr      .
       car-dti-dcp-ubi-620.
           add       1                    to   w-det-gia-ubi-ctr      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
